        <body>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;New functionality has just been introduced that provides you with ability to add one or more Lodgement Points to a Credit&amp;nbsp;Management Request (Work Type = Add Lodgement Point).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Where four or more lodgement points have been raised to a Credit&amp;nbsp;Management Request, they will be automatically routed to a new queue&amp;nbsp;managed by the Credit Risk team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;What does this mean for me?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Deal Support Request (DSR) Users/Sales Account Managers - You can add multiple lodgement points utilising new&amp;nbsp;functionality built into the ‘Add lodgement point’&amp;nbsp;credit work type request,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;AP Type Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(8, 7, 7);&quot;&gt;rather than creating a new request for each lodgement point you want to add to a related billing account.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</body>
